<TEXT>
wheelingpittsburgh steel corp says it has 
submitted its initial plan for reorganization to the us bankruptcy 
court here 
a broad outline of the plan which had been circulated earlier to 
the media said the reorganization would reduce the companys 
current common stockholders ownership to 7 percent 
both wheelingpittsburgh and lawyers close to the reorganization 
now nearly four years in progress said the final plan would likely 
look much different than the one submitted thursday 
the initial plan is seen as a starting point for negotiations 
among the companys creditors employee groups and stockholders 
</TEXT>
